root: ^I can’t stand those hipsters screaming all day.
^And the boss has to deal even with the lawyer of those who harass us since last year. They keep blaming us for everything. They must be desperate for fame.
^Well, at least in his office this noise can’t be heard. If I hear more about trees I’ll go crazy.
^Damn it, I told you not to put it on the edge! Help me clean up.
